					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It's hard to say, I was impressed to see how Castlevania 3 looks better with them, while it doesn't affect this much some other games. Super C and games of the Gradius series also looks significantly better with them. Batman looks much better, too.
<br />
<br />Final Fantasy games looks quite better without them I think, but I don't know much why.
<br />I guess games with dark graphics looks better with them, while dark with more fantasic graphics looks better without them.</div>

